	<h1 class="title">「这世界」有人做拍卖40年，还是被女王内裤惊到了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-10-29 11:49:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3138/medium/3138.jpg?1436636665" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


